---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const basePath = baseUrl.endsWith('/') ? baseUrl : `${baseUrl}/`;
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Robert Otieno" description="About Robert Otieno, Enterprise Identity, Security & IT Operations Architect.">
	<section class="profile-section">
		<div class="profile-container">
			<div class="profile-header">
				<h1>Robert Otieno</h1>
				<p class="profile-title">Enterprise Identity, Security & IT Operations Architect</p>
				<div class="profile-meta">
					<span class="meta-item">📍 Copenhagen, Denmark</span>
					<span class="meta-item">🇰🇪 Kenyan</span>
					<span class="meta-item">⚡ Age 32</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="profile-grid">
				<div class="profile-bio">
					<h2>About Me</h2>
					<p>
						From competitive football to enterprise security architecture — the arena changed, but the ambition only grew. With roots in Nyakach, Kisumu County, Kenya, I developed discipline and competitive drive early. Football shaped my mindset: structure matters, positioning matters, and performance is earned. I still play — because high standards are maintained, not remembered.
					</p>
					<p>
						My technology journey began in Kenya, building foundations in systems and infrastructure. It accelerated in Denmark, where I deepened my focus on identity architecture, zero-trust security, and privacy-engineered systems.
					</p>
					<p>
						Today, I design IAM, IGA, PAM, and decentralized identity solutions that align governance with business strategy. But I'm not interested in maintaining systems — I aspire to build more. More resilient architectures. More intelligent trust frameworks. More scalable identity ecosystems that redefine how organizations operate securely.
					</p>
					<p>
						The field changed. The ambition expanded. And I'm building at a higher level.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="profile-education">
					<h2>Education & Background</h2>
					
					<div class="education-item">
						<h3>MSc Engineering in Innovative Communication Technologies & Entrepreneurship</h3>
						<p class="education-meta">Aalborg University Copenhagen · Denmark</p>
						<p>Advanced study in communication technologies, innovation-driven entrepreneurship, and emerging tech solutions.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="education-item">
						<h3>Bachelor of Science in Information Technology</h3>
						<p class="education-meta">Jomo Kenyatta University of Agriculture & Technology · Jun 2022</p>
						<p>Based in Nairobi, Kenya. Foundation in software development, systems architecture, and IT infrastructure.</p>
					</div>
					
					<h3 style="margin-top: 1.8rem; color: #1e3a8a;">Interests & Passions</h3>
					<ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 0.8rem;">
						<li>⚽ Football enthusiast & Manchester United supporter</li>
						<li>🔐 Enterprise security and identity architecture</li>
						<li>🚀 Technology innovation and emerging standards</li>
						<li>🌍 Building resilient systems for global enterprises</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="career-section">
		<h2>Career Journey</h2>
		<div class="career-grid">
			<article class="career-card">
				<h3>IT Support Specialist</h3>
				<p class="career-meta">Pandora A/S · Copenhagen, Denmark</p>
				<p>Enterprise IT operations, system governance, and operational security support for global infrastructure.</p>
			</article>
			
			<article class="career-card">
				<h3>Internet of Things Research Assistant</h3>
				<p class="career-meta">Aalborg University · Denmark</p>
				<p>Research in IoT systems, connected infrastructure, and emerging technology applications.</p>
			</article>
			
			<article class="career-card">
				<h3>Information Technology Specialist</h3>
				<p class="career-meta">Secope Solutions LTD · Kisumu, Kenya</p>
				<p>IT consulting, system integration, and technology solutions for regional enterprises.</p>
			</article>
			
			<article class="career-card">
				<h3>IT Operations Specialist</h3>
				<p class="career-meta">Acacia Premier Hotel · Kenya</p>
				<p>Operational IT management, infrastructure maintenance, and guest services technology support.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="principles-section">
		<h2>Core Principles</h2>
		<p class="section-intro">Four foundational pillars that guide my approach to enterprise identity architecture and security design.</p>
		<div class="principles-grid">
			<article class="principle-card">
				<div class="principle-number">01</div>
				<h3>Identity as Control Plane</h3>
				<p>Security posture starts with reliable identity context and consistent access decisions.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="principle-card">
				<div class="principle-number">02</div>
				<h3>Operational Integration</h3>
				<p>Policy value is realized only when IAM controls are embedded in incident and change workflows.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="principle-card">
				<div class="principle-number">03</div>
				<h3>Privacy by Architecture</h3>
				<p>Privacy is treated as a design constraint, not an afterthought, with explicit minimization choices.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="principle-card">
				<div class="principle-number">04</div>
				<h3>Automation for Scale</h3>
				<p>Governance must be repeatable, auditable, and operationally sustainable across enterprise growth.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="direction-section">
		<div class="direction-container">
			<div class="direction-badge">Current Focus</div>
			<h2>Where I'm Building Next</h2>
			<p class="direction-content">
				I am focused on enterprise IAM modernization, access governance transformation, and practical pathways for decentralized identity in
				real-world organizations. My work centers on bridging the gap between emerging identity standards and operational realities — building systems that scale without sacrificing security or privacy.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.profile-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8faff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
	}

	.profile-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.profile-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #1e3a8a;
	}

	.profile-header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.profile-title {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.profile-meta {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.meta-item {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #475569;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.profile-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	.profile-bio h2,
	.profile-education h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1.2rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #1e3a8a;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.profile-bio p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #334155;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
	}

	.profile-bio p:last-of-type {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.education-item {
		margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
	}

	.education-item h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.education-meta {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 0.6rem 0;
	}

	.education-item p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.education-item ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0 0;
	}

	.education-item ul li {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #334155;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.education-item ul li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.profile-education h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.profile-education ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.profile-education ul li {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #334155;
		padding-left: 1.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
		position: relative;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.profile-education ul li::before {
		content: "→";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.career-section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.career-section h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-bottom: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.career-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.career-card {
		background: #ffffff;
		border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.08);
	}

	.career-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.15);
		border-color: #1e3a8a;
	}

	.career-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.career-meta {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
	}

	.career-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.principles-section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.principles-section h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-bottom: 3px solid #1e3a8a;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.section-intro {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #475569;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.principles-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.principle-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8faff 100%);
		border: 2px solid #e0e7ff;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.8rem;
		position: relative;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.principle-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 4px;
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
		transform: scaleY(0);
		transform-origin: bottom;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.principle-card:hover::before {
		transform: scaleY(1);
		transform-origin: top;
	}

	.principle-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.15);
		border-color: #1e3a8a;
	}

	.principle-number {
		display: inline-block;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #1e3a8a;
		opacity: 0.2;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
		font-family: monospace;
		letter-spacing: -0.05em;
	}

	.principle-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.principle-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.direction-section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #2563eb 100%);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		color: #ffffff;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.direction-section::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 300px;
		height: 300px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
		border-radius: 50%;
		transform: translate(40%, -40%);
	}

	.direction-container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		max-width: 900px;
	}

	.direction-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		color: #ffffff;
		padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.direction-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 1.2rem 0;
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.direction-content {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.profile-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.career-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.principles-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.profile-meta {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.8rem;
		}

		.profile-header h1 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.profile-section {
			padding: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.profile-header {
			margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
			padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.profile-header h1 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.profile-title {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}

		.profile-meta {
			gap: 0.8rem;
		}

		.meta-item {
			font-size: 0.85rem;
		}
	}
</style>